Set Up a Meta Ads Connection

Create a Meta Ads connection to use as a data source in Salesforce Data Cloud.

In Data Cloud, click Setup, and select Data Cloud Setup.
Under Configuration, click More Connectors.
Click New. 
From the Source tab, select the Meta Ads connector, and then click Next.
.Enter the connection name and connection API name.
Select the named credential that you created
Enter your Meta customer ID
Save your changes.
To review your configuration, click Test Connection.
Click Save.
After the connector details are accepted, it’s listed under More Connectors and ready to use.
